# Cursor Rules for HeyJ Project

## MCP Configuration
- Supabase MCP is configured in `.cursor/mcp.json`
- Replace `YOUR_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY_HERE` with your actual service role key from Supabase dashboard

## Database Schema
- The `profiles` table should have a `userCode` column (TEXT type)
- userCode format: `Name@1234` (name without spaces + @ + 4-digit number)

## Code Style
- Use TypeScript with React Native
- Follow existing code patterns in the project
